OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1773111798
OL,3,CMiscarriage services 'dismissive and
OL,4,Cdehumanising' in UK
OL,6,FSuffering a miscarriage is still a
OL,7,F"dismissive and dehumanising"
OL,8,Fexperience in the UK, with women at
OL,9,Ffurther risk of harm and distress due
OL,10,Fto inadequate follow-up care, a report
OL,11,Fhas found.
OL,13,FResearch published by the Miscarriage
OL,14,FAssociation showed that 65% of women
OL,15,Flacked access to suitable follow-up
OL,16,Fcare after pregnancy loss, while more
OL,17,F42% did not receive treatment for
OL,18,Fmental health symptoms.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1773111798
OL,3,CMiscarriage services 'dismissive and
OL,4,Cdehumanising' in UK
OL,6,FThe report described a continuous
OL,7,F"lack of dignity", including
OL,8,Fencountering insensitive wording from
OL,9,Fhealthcare professionals, with one
OL,10,Fwoman told her baby "had been put in
OL,11,Fthe incinerator with the rest of the
OL,12,Fmedical waste" whilst recovering from
OL,13,Fa ruptured ectopic pregnancy.
OL,15,F"Too many women and their partners are
OL,16,Fbeing failed by a system that is
OL,17,Finconsistent, unequal and too often
OL,18,Fdictated by chance or circumstance,"
OL,19,FVicki Robinson, chief executive of the
OL,20,FMiscarriage Association, said.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@QO]rD@UOUtD@NO]wD@AOUzD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1773111798
OL,3,CMiscarriage services 'dismissive and
OL,4,Cdehumanising' in UK
OL,6,F"People told us they felt unheard and
OL,7,Fdiminished, caught between gaps in
OL,8,Fhealthcare, uncertainty at work, and a
OL,9,Fwider silence that leaves miscarriage
OL,10,Fpoorly understood and acknowledged."
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1773111798
OL,3,CMiscarriage services 'dismissive and
OL,4,Cdehumanising' in UK
OL,6,FThe new report, which is backed by MPs
OL,7,Fand presenter Myleene Klass, is
OL,8,Fcalling for urgent action to ensure
OL,9,Ffollow-up care after a miscarriage is
OL,10,Froutine. The research included more
OL,11,Fthan 1,000 people in the UK impacted
OL,12,Fby miscarriage before the 24th week of
OL,13,Fpregnancy.
OL,15,FHalf of respondents described their
OL,16,Fcare as good or excellent, but more
OL,17,Fthan a quarter said it was poor or
OL,18,Fvery poor. Almost 80% of them sought
OL,19,Fmedical support from an NHS hospital,
OL,20,Fnotably an early pregnancy unit.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1773111798
OL,3,CMiscarriage services 'dismissive and
OL,4,Cdehumanising' in UK
OL,6,FMany felt they were sent home with
OL,7,Flittle or no guidance, or with
OL,8,Fconflicting advice, the Miscarriage
OL,9,FAssociation said.
OL,11,F"This is not about blaming
OL,12,Findividuals. Many examples of
OL,13,Fcompassionate care exist, and we are
OL,14,Fworking to build on these through our
OL,15,Ffree specialist training for
OL,16,Fhealthcare professionals," Robinson
OL,17,Fsaid.
OL,26,@sD@AOUxD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1773111798
OL,3,CMiscarriage services 'dismissive and
OL,4,Cdehumanising' in UK
OL,6,F"But when support depends on where you
OL,7,Fare, who you speak to, or how well
OL,8,Fsystems join up, too many people are
OL,9,Fleft facing additional physical harm
OL,10,Fand lasting psychological distress at
OL,11,Fan already vulnerable time."
OL,13,FMore than two-thirds of women said
OL,14,Fthey experienced mental health
OL,15,Fproblems connected with their
OL,16,Fmiscarriage, including grief,
OL,17,Fdepression, PTSD, and suicidal
OL,18,Fthoughts, the report found.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1773111798
OL,3,CMiscarriage services 'dismissive and
OL,4,Cdehumanising' in UK
OL,6,FIt also described a lack of dignity as
OL,7,Fa "recurring theme", with some women
OL,8,Fleft without access to basic care,
OL,9,Fsuch as sanitary pads.
OL,11,FThe research included experiences of
OL,12,Fmiscarriage and the workplace, and
OL,13,Fnoted that employees' rights around
OL,14,Fpregnancy are "poorly understood".
OL,15,FFear of stigma or career impact still
OL,16,Fprevents people from openly discussing
OL,17,Fthe issue, it said.
OL,26,@vD@OOUvD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1773111798
OL,3,CMiscarriage services 'dismissive and
OL,4,Cdehumanising' in UK
OL,6,FThe Miscarriage Association has
OL,7,Frecommended services ensure follow-up
OL,8,Fcare becomes routine for every
OL,9,Fmiscarriage, with cover for physical
OL,10,Frecovery, complications such as
OL,11,Finfections or anaemia, psychological
OL,12,Fwellbeing and referrals for further
OL,13,Fsupport, where necessary.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1773111798
OL,3,CMiscarriage services 'dismissive and
OL,4,Cdehumanising' in UK
OL,6,FIt also called for more bereavement
OL,7,Fsupport and the right to bereavement
OL,8,Fleave to be implemented within
OL,9,Fworkplaces, as well as extended
OL,10,Fopening hours at early pregnancy
OL,11,Funits, to ensure more access to timely
OL,12,Fcare, and specialist training for
OL,13,Fhealthcare professionals.
OL,15,F"Clear, consistent aftercare following
OL,16,Fpregnancy loss should be available to
OL,17,Fall," Robinson said.
OL,26,@wD@AOUyD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1773111798
OL,3,CMiscarriage services 'dismissive and
OL,4,Cdehumanising' in UK
OL,6,F"Until pregnancy loss is properly
OL,7,Facknowledged, too many people will
OL,8,Fcontinue to face miscarriage without
OL,9,Fthe care, support and recognition they
OL,10,Fneed and deserve."
OL,12,FKlass is a champion of the Miscarriage
OL,13,FAssociation and received an MBE for
OL,14,Fher campaigning after sharing her own
OL,15,Fexperience of multiple pregnancy
OL,16,Flosses.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31811
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1773111798
OL,3,CMiscarriage services 'dismissive and
OL,4,Cdehumanising' in UK
OL,6,F"Pregnancy loss is not a niche issue,
OL,7,Fit affects thousands each year, yet
OL,8,Fmany still struggle to access the care
OL,9,Fand understanding they deserve," Klass
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,F"This research by the Miscarriage
OL,13,FAssociation is an important step in
OL,14,Fholding the system to account and
OL,15,Fpushing for meaningful change. We must
OL,16,Flisten to those with lived experience
OL,17,Fand make miscarriage care a priority."
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@`O]tD@AOUyD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31812
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1773111798
OL,3,CMiscarriage services 'dismissive and
OL,4,Cdehumanising' in UK
OL,6,FA spokesperson at the Department of
OL,7,FHealth and Social Care described
OL,8,Flosing a baby as "heartbreaking" and
OL,9,Fsaid the report's findings were
OL,10,F"unacceptable".
OL,12,F"We are working to improve miscarriage
OL,13,Fcare to ensure women get the support
OL,14,Fthey need, and we have already
OL,15,Fextended the reach of baby loss
OL,16,Fcertificates to provide the
OL,17,Frecognition that can mean so much to
OL,18,Faffected families," they said.
OL,26,@pD@ROUpD@`O]rD@AOUrD@NO]tD@AOUzD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
